column63: There is increased speculation of large sized factory tenders to SELL electricity into the local market.

Given the expected supply and demand in the market, the Regulatory Authority for Electricity board expects that the price for tomorrow will be between $17.00 and $22.00.

There will be 500 contracts available in the entire ELEC market, 250 contracts for buying and 250 contracts for selling. There are a total of 19 Producers, 19 Distributors and 38 Traders in the market.

Please note that the RAE will charge a bid-ask spread of 1 cent
